Estetinis idstymas

Klases idstome spalv skalje

 ggplot(data = mpg) + 
    geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = class))

Klases idstome dydi skalje

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
     geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, size = class))

Kitos skals idstymui

# alpha  permatomumo skal
ggplot(data = mpg) + 
    geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, alpha = class)) 

# shape  form skal
 ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, shape = class))

Estetini savybi parinkimas rankiniu bdu

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
     geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy), color = "blue")

Kaip nurodyti spalvas?

Spalv kod parinkimas: https://www.w3schools.com/colors/colors_picker.asp

Uduotys: estetinis idstymas

  1. Kur kode klaida? Kodl takai ne mlyni? Itaisykite.
ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy), color = "blue")

  1. Kurie lentels mpg kintamieji yra kategoriniai? Kurie tolydieji? (Uuomina: ?mpg). Kaip tai pamatyti atspausdinus mpg?
?mpg
  1. Pasirinkite tolydj kintamj ir atidkite jo reikmes iose skalse: color, size, shape.
ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, size = year))

ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = year))

  1. Kuo i estetikos element (color, size, shape) idstymas skiriasi, jei atidedame kategorin vs. tolydj kintamj?
ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = year))

ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = class))

  1. K daro estetikos elementas stroke? Su kuriomis formomis jis veikia? (Uuomina: naudokite geom_point).
ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = class, stroke = year))

  1. Kas nutinka, jei naudojate kelias skales (pvz., color, size) su keliais skirtingais kintamaisiais?
ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = year, size = class))

  1. Kas nutinka, jei to paties kintamojo reikmes atidedate keliose skirtingose skalse (tarkime, color ir shape)?
ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = class, shape = class))

  1. Kas nutinka, jei su tam tikra skale susiejate ne konkretaus kintamojo pavadinim (pvz., aes(colour = displ)), o kok nors veiksm su tuo kintamuoju, tarkime aes(colour = displ < 5)?
ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color = displ < 5))

  1. Nubraiykite grafik ir jame rankiniu bdu parinkite spakvas naudodami:
    • spalv pavadinimus (rayti kabtse);
    • eioliktainius kodus (rayti kabutse);
    • spalv numerius tarp 1 ir 8, be kabui.
